        <mxCell id="w99l4QLJi8G1Wg-2OeCw-4" value="&lt;div style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Calibri, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;??&amp;quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Inter, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; class=&quot;el-h2&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-block-start: var(--p-spacing); margin-block-end: var(--p-spacing); --font-weight: var(--h2-weight); font-variant: var(--h2-variant); letter-spacing: -0.015em; line-height: var(--h2-line-height); color: var(--h2-color); font-style: var(--h2-style); font-family: var(--h2-font); margin-top: var(--heading-spacing);&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; data-heading=&quot;1. 总体分数&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: var(--h2-color); font-family: var(--h2-font); font-style: var(--h2-style); letter-spacing: -0.015em;&quot;&gt;1. 总体分数&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Calibri, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;??&amp;quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Inter, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; class=&quot;el-ul&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding-inline-start: 0px; margin-block-start: var(--p-spacing); margin-block-end: var(--p-spacing); list-style-type: &amp;quot;​&amp;quot;;&quot; class=&quot;has-list-bullet&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-align: start; padding-top: var(--list-spacing); padding-bottom: var(--list-spacing); position: relative; margin-inline-start: 3ch;&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; data-line=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: transparent; position: relative; display: inline-flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; float: inline-start; margin-inline-start: -0.8em;&quot; class=&quot;list-bullet&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; opacity: 0; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; position: absolute; cursor: var(--cursor); user-select: none; margin-inline-start: -2.65em; padding-inline-end: 2em;&quot; class=&quot;list-collapse-indicator collapse-indicator collapse-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;svg class=&quot;svg-icon right-triangle&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M3 8L12 17L21 8&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--bold-color);&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--code-normal); font-family: var(--font-monospace); background-color: var(--code-background); border-radius: var(--code-radius); padding: 0.15em 0.3em; border: var(--code-border-width) solid var(--code-border-color); -webkit-box-decoration-break: clone;&quot;&gt;&quot;score&quot;: 4.338572267534316&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: &amp;quot;​&amp;quot;; padding-inline-start: 0px; position: relative;&quot; class=&quot;has-list-bullet&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-align: start; padding-top: var(--list-spacing); padding-bottom: var(--list-spacing); position: relative; margin-inline-start: var(--list-indent);&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; data-line=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: transparent; position: relative; display: inline-flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; float: inline-start; margin-inline-start: -0.8em;&quot; class=&quot;list-bullet&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;这是最终的 BLEU-4 分数，值为 4.34（通常表示为 4.34 BLEU）&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-align: start; padding-top: var(--list-spacing); padding-bottom: var(--list-spacing); position: relative; margin-inline-start: var(--list-indent);&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; data-line=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: transparent; position: relative; display: inline-flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; float: inline-start; margin-inline-start: -0.8em;&quot; class=&quot;list-bullet&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;范围在 0-100 之间，数值越高表示机器翻译结果与参考翻译越接近&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-align: start; padding-top: var(--list-spacing); padding-bottom: var(--list-spacing); position: relative; margin-inline-start: var(--list-indent);&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; data-line=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: transparent; position: relative; display: inline-flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; float: inline-start; margin-inline-start: -0.8em;&quot; class=&quot;list-bullet&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;这个分数相对较低，说明翻译质量有待提高&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Calibri, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;??&amp;quot;, ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Inter, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; class=&quot;el-h2&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-block-start: var(--p-spacing); margin-block-end: var(--p-spacing); --font-weight: var(--h2-weight); font-variant: var(